{"lemma":"عِصْمَة","slug":"عِصْمَة","root":"ع.ص.م","root_slug":"ع-ص-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ص-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n29374","n29375"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%90%D8%B5%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"defense; protection"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"chastity, purity, modesty, virtuousness"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"infallibility; the inability to issue a wrong teaching (as e.g. of the Shiite imams or Catholic popes)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"infallibility; the inability to issue a wrong teaching (as e.g. of the Shiite imams or Catholic popes); 'ismah"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʕisˤ.ma/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n29374","headword_ar":"عُصْمَةٌ","root":"ESm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qilaAdap","text_ar":"قِلَادَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collar"},{"kind":"text","text":"for a dog]: (S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSomapN","text_ar":"عِصْمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Kr, K, &c.;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling a bracelet:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA:) pl. (of the latter, TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSamN","text_ar":"عِصَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and pl. pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoSumN","text_ar":"اَعْصُمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSamapN","text_ar":"عِصَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSamapN","text_ar":"عَصَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but, as is said in the TA, with kesr and then fet-h], and pl. pl. pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoSaAmN","text_ar":"اَعْصَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) or this last, which is said in the S to be pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuSompN","text_ar":"عُصْمةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and thought by ISd to be formed from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSomapN","text_ar":"عِصْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"after rejecting the augmentative letter ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and said by some to be a pl. of which the sing. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSomN","text_ar":"عِصْمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEodaAlN","text_ar":"اَعْدَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EidolN","text_ar":"عِدْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is correctly pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSamN","text_ar":"عِصَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSomapN","text_ar":"عِصْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IB, TA.) of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoSimapN","text_ar":"اَعْصِمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also a pl. [of pauc.] (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoSaAmN","text_ar":"اَعْصَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"straps"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea*abaAt","text_ar":"عَذَبَات"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that are upon the necks"},{"kind":"text","text":"of dogs: and the sing, is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuSomapN","text_ar":"عُصْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and, (K, TA,) some say, (TA,) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSaAmN","text_ar":"عِصَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) with kesr, [in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSAmN","text_ar":"عَصامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] mentioned by Lth. (TA.) [Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaEotuhu A_ilayohi biEuSomatihi","text_ar":"دَفَعْتُهُ اـِلَيْهِ بِعُصْمَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biEiSaAmihi","text_ar":"بِعِصَامِهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I gave it to him altogether"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; like as one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"birum~atihi","text_ar":"بِرُمَّتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (TA.)       -A2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quality denoted by the epithet"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoSamu","text_ar":"اَعْصَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (S, K:) ISh says, it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the arm of the gazelle"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the mountain-goat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and IAar says, it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in cloven-hoofed animals in the fare legs;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the crow, in the shanks;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and sometimes, he says, it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in horses."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S"]},{"entry_id":"n29375","headword_ar":"عِصْمَةٌ","root":"ESm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[mentioned in the Mgh as an inf. n., but said in the Msb to be a simple subst.,] primarily (TA) signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manoEN","text_ar":"مَنْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Prevention,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hindrance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as seems to be indicated by most of its subordinate applications,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"protection"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, K, TA:) or, as some say, its primary signification is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"act of tying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"binding;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence the meaning of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manoEN","text_ar":"مَنْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, accord. to Zj, it primarily signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabolN","text_ar":"حَبْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a rope,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cord"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and accord. to Mohammad Ibn-Neshwán El- Himyeree,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sababN","text_ar":"سَبَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabolN","text_ar":"حَبْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which mean the same]. (TA.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Defence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"protection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preservation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,) [in an absolute sense, and] as an act of God, (Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from that which would cause destruction"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a man. (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSomapu","text_ar":"عِصْمَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^anobiyaA='i","text_ar":"الاَنْبِيَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies God's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preservation of the prophets;"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2067},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first, by the peculiar endowment of them with essential purity of constitution; then, by the conferring of large and highly-esteemed excellences; then, by aid against opponents, and rendering their feet firm; then, by sending down upon them tranquillity"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~akiynap","text_ar":"السَّكِينَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.), [see the Kur ix. 26, &c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the preservation of their hearts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"minds, and adaptation to that which is right."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rá- ghib, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A defence"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a defender from a state of perdition"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from want:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in a saying of Aboo-Tálib, in praise of the Prophet, cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vimaAlN","text_ar":"ثِمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A faculty of avoiding,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shunning, acts of disobedience,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of self-preservation therefrom,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with possession of power to commit them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Muná- wee, TA:) [or,] as used by the Muslim theologians,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inability to disobey:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a disposition that prevents"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disobedience"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not such as constrains"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to act"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (MF, TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSomapu Aln~ikaAHi","text_ar":"عِصْمَةُ النِّكَاحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The tie,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bond, of marriage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[also called, in the present day,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSomapu AlmaroA^api","text_ar":"عِصْمَةُ المَرْاَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the woman's matrimonial tie"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bond, which is in her husband's hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"power:"},{"kind":"text","text":"a term used by the lawyers:] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biyadihi EiSomapu Aln~ikaAHi","text_ar":"بِيَدِهِ عِصْمَةُ النِّكَاحِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In his hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"power, is"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the tie,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bond, of marriage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSamN","text_ar":"عِصَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": whence, in the Kur [lx. 10],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaA tumas~ikuwA","text_ar":"وَلَا تُمَسِّكُوا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biEiSami AlkawaAfiri","text_ar":"بِعِصَمِ الكَوَافِرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And hold ye not to the matrimonial ties,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bonds, of the unbelieving women;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning divorce ye such women: but the common reading is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wlA tumosikuwA","text_ar":"ولا تُمْسِكُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":", which signifies the same]. (TA.) ―         -b5-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuSomapN","text_ar":"عُصْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["TA","S","K","Msb"]}]}}